      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must have documented V&V test suite and version-controlled release process consistent with MRL 2 requirements.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023 R2 employed with ISO 9001-certified QMS. Solver regression test suite of 847 benchmark cases executed at each release. Version control via Git with signed commits. SQA documentation reviewed and found compliant with MRL 2 requirements."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate correct implementation of governing equations through method-of-manufactured-solutions or equivalent benchmark comparisons at MRL 2 level.",
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions applied to incompressible Navier-Stokes solver confirming second-order spatial accuracy. Benchmark comparisons against lid-driven cavity and backward-facing step canonical flows show <1% deviation from published reference solutions."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) < 5% for all quantities of interest at required operating points.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study yields GCI = 1.8% for NIH and GCI = 1.4% for peak wall shear stress at worst-case operating point (4 L/min, 3500 RPM). Richardson extrapolation confirms asymptotic convergence regime. Achieved level exceeds MRL 2 requirement."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
