    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 requirements. Validation evidence demonstrates NIH prediction error of 8.3% (within 15% acceptance criterion) and RH = 0.87 < 1.0 at worst-case operating condition. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB use conditions. Package accepted for regulatory submission support.",
